## Controller mapping

| Input | Action |
| ----- | ------ |
| D-pad / left stick | Navigate (spatial focus) |
| A / Cross | Select / Confirm |
| B / Circle | Back |
| X / Square | Edit properties |
| Y / Triangle | Add game journey |
| L1 / R1 | Switch sections (home â†” library â†” search) |
| Menu / Options | Settings |

Keyboard fallback: arrows, Enter, Escape, `F` (edit), `C` (add), `[` `]`, `M`.

Controller family detection (Xbox / PlayStation / Nintendo) swaps confirm/back on Nintendo.
See `src/controllers/ControllerMapping.ts`.

