## Data model (SQLite)

| Table | Purpose |
| ----- | ------- |
| `games` | Library entries â€” title, provider, platform, launch JSON, artwork JSON, playtime, achievements |
| `import_sources` | Registered importer paths per provider |
| `play_sessions` | Launch/stop history with PID, duration, exit code |
| `settings` | Key/value JSON (theme id, API keys) |
| `collections` / `collection_games` | Future grouping (schema present) |
| `user_overrides` | Per-game override JSON |
| `schema_migrations` | Migration versioning |

Database path: `~/Library/Application Support/Orbit/orbit.db` (see `src-tauri/src/utils/paths.rs`).

Artwork is stored as Base64 inside `artwork_json` on each game row.

